text: == Events == * The caliph al-Muti is overthrown from the Abbasid Caliphate and replaced by his son al-Ta'i who died shortly after his son's takeover. * An earthquake happens in England which kills 600 people. * The Liao dynasty switches ambassadors between the Song dynasty on New Year's Day. * The city of Fuzhou starts to build new walls. == References == Category:970s
